channel.description: how do i add doors to a pi server? I added something in actionhandler but all it does is it goes through the door(door dont even open) but u cant get in the other way. Also when it says c.object==9168 c.object==3218 (something like that) what does this mean?

item.title: Help plz
item.dc:creator: @Sanskrit Sanskrit
item.description:
@Sanskrit wrote:

breaking down “c.object==9168”:
“c.”: c stands for client.
“object”: variable for global objects.
“==”: The equal to operator.
“9168”: The object id.

Im sure there is a tut somewhere on adding doors, just use the search button ;D
